description: Need a good meal? Almost all of Alameda alleges that this All-American Airstream Trailer is where you find the “Best Burger in the Bay Area”, so you all better start making your way over. Scolari’s Good Eats is also grilling up all your favorite American classic treats, like Chicken Wings, Italian Sandwiches, Hot Dogs, and is it really any surprise that you can also find fantastic fries?Come out to Scolari’s Good Eats for some of the best food you’ll find on the streets.
name: Scolari's Good Eats
